beer.beer_description:
Originally brewed as a seasonal small batch keg release, we are now bottling this behemoth.

Our American IPA is all about hops, malt and even more hops! We use over 20kg per brew for this enamel reducing ale and the fantastic malt backbone allows the lupulins to do their worst.

Flavours of tangerine, pine needle, grapefruit and biscuit all meld together into perfect (trans)fusion.
